data.name: InitializationErrorMessage
data.value: `.UseMauiCommunityToolkit()` is required to initalize .NET MAUI Community Toolkit.

data.name: AttachedBindablePropertyDefaultValueCreatorMessageFormat
data.value: Method '{0}' returns a static readonly field or property. This will cause all instances to share the same reference. Return a new instance instead.

data.name: AttachedBindablePropertyDefaultValueCreatorErrorMessage
data.value: DefaultValueCreatorMethodName methods must return a new instance, not a static readonly field or property, to ensure each BindableObject receives a unique instance.
